{"tid":2246730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"愛豆圈的「人間富貴花」：Mina、Jennie、Minnie、Lia她們的臉上寫著貴氣的高級臉","createTime":"2020-10-17T09:57:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T02:37:36.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"40919bb5bf6b9aa9c6b2528a0fc9dad0066b146b","tid":2246730,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T09:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_13bd88dcb91e2ac485f02fa59532cdb0/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-14/130855-880108.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_13bd88dcb91e2ac485f02fa59532cdb0%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-14%2F130855-880108.png&h=ecc1c64c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誇讚一個女生的形容詞有很多，今天小編就來說說最近很火的「人間富貴花」。<br />\n<br />\n人間富貴花從字面上理解，就是那種長相中充滿了貴氣的人，一眼看來就是從小就嬌養長大，愛豆圈裡能被冠上這個稱號的有哪些人呢?<br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK Jennie<br />\n<br />\n唱跳俱佳的Jennie顏值也是相當的高，氣質冷艷，特別會駕馭性感與野性兼並的穿搭。 被叫「人間香奈兒」不是沒有理由的，高貴氣質即使是在花田一般的女愛豆圈也不多見，一看就是嬌養出來的富家千金。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_50192db270d8d2563466e98d7cfb4af4/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-14/130855-880078.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_50192db270d8d2563466e98d7cfb4af4%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-14%2F130855-880078.jpeg&h=7016dd04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWICE MINA<br />\n<br />\nMINA的大小姐氣質和Jennie完全不是一路的，貴氣中帶著柔美，我見憐猶型，像極了被富養長大的小公主，不用為了生計奔波，永遠被保護在小窩裡。 而MINA確實家境優渥，她的高中就讀日本著名的貴族學校，父親是原來是一名著名的醫學教授。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ddfa75fdd8e78812cc005a9ca6a45fa6/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-14/130855-880081.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ddfa75fdd8e78812cc005a9ca6a45fa6%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-14%2F130855-880081.jpeg&h=80211401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(G)I-DLE Minnie<br />\n<br />\n氣質、身材和顏值上Minnie無可挑剔，尤其是五官大氣又明艷，很像泰劇裡的嬌氣又有些刁蠻的大小姐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_40465b9c92d891ee757f8a742c95a12a/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-14/130855-880084.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_40465b9c92d891ee757f8a742c95a12a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-14%2F130855-880084.jpeg&h=c22c7b4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nITZY Lia<br />\n<br />\nLia的五官更有肉感一些，她的眉眼之間，眼波流動中都是淡淡的嬌貴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e21958034cbbcabcba00285bd5b61c91/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-14/130855-880087.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e21958034cbbcabcba00285bd5b61c91%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-14%2F130855-880087.jpeg&h=34880f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「圖：NATE PHOTOS、theqoo」"},{"pid":"fc9740a0b43cf9a71bfd9abea8e8cadcc6119bf5","tid":2246730,"uid":136770,"like":38,"dislike":14,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:00:20.000Z","msg":"Mina<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LO9son3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLO9son3.jpg&h=f540ffa8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4a42119671c0c04faedac24bd0f138299e364ee","tid":2246730,"uid":294121,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:00:22.000Z","msg":"共通點係4個都係無波<br />\njennie已經係最大個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4885466b1a212f71ad51a09d9ba5a0336333eece","tid":2246730,"uid":34489,"like":15,"dislike":7,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T10:01:14.000Z","msg":"mina成面墨屎..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c26a8c39cdc1321840af6934dd69a7fda3d0c2","tid":2246730,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c4a42119671c0c04faedac24bd0f138299e364ee","tid":2246730,"uid":294121,"like":18